Superstition is a music track that is unlocked inside the top floor of the Viyeldi Caves, or in the Tower of Magic prison.

Versions[edit | edit source]

Version Release Music Track
2 June – September 2004
3 6 March 2007

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Before the track was released, Voodoo Cult played at this location.
  • According to data crowdsourced via RuneLite, approximately 76% of players unlock the track in the Viyeldi Caves, while 24% unlock it in the Tower of Magic.
